name: A Letter to 2022
description:
Hi Metaverse, Hi 2022
To let it go it's the hardest part, we know
but chin up, and smile.

Don't force anything,
let it go, let it flow,

Enjoy every little feeling
Enjoy every little achievement 
Enjoy it.

Be thankful and 
believe that every miracle or magic will come to your life.










Visual: Aloysius Nitia
Music : Aloysius Nitia and Anggi Faradilla
